al-stream/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:4945:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/jquery_social_stream.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into a single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Includes 13 social networks with a total of 24 different feed options.</p>\n<p>Using only jQuery, the social stream plugin can be used for ANY website &#8230; including WordPress &#8230; no PHP required!</p>\n<p><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">View jQuery Social Stream Plugin Demo Site</a></p>\n<h3>Plugin Supports 13 Social Networks</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter &#8211; Latest Tweets</li>\n<li>Facebook &#8211; Page Latest Wall Posts</li>\n<li>Google +1 &#8211; Latest +1 Posts</li>\n<li>RSS Feed &#8211; Latest Posts</li>\n<li>Delicious &#8211; Latest Likes</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon &#8211; Favorites or Reviews</li>\n<li>Pinterest &#8211; Latest Pins</li>\n<li>Dribbble &#8211; Latest Shots or Likes</li>\n<li>Youtube &#8211; Latest Uploads or Favorites</li>\n<li>Vimeo &#8211; Likes, Videos, Appeared In, Albums, Channels or Groups</li>\n<li>Flickr &#8211; Latest Uploads</li>\n<li>last.fm &#8211; Loved Tracks, Recent Tracks or Reply Tracker</li>\n<li>Deviantart &#8211; Latest Deviations</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Social Stream Display Options</h3>\n<p>Display using rotating feed list or a filterable jQuery Isotope powered Social Network Wall!</p>\n<div style="float: left;">\n<p><strong>Includes 2 sample skins for the rotating list:</strong></p>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/dcsns_feed.png" alt="jQuery Social Stream Feed" class="img-border" /></div>\n<div style="float: right;">\n<p><strong>Pinterest style Social Network Wall:</strong></p>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/dcsns_wall.png" alt="j